OL,6,FAnd too much of its positive
OL,7,Freputation inside and outside the UK
OL,8,Fcan still rely on memories of The
OL,9,FBeatles ` 53 years after they split
OL,10,Fup.
OL,12,FHopefully Eurovision fans and
OL,13,Fdelegates will return home and
OL,14,Frecommend Liverpool to their friends.
OL,3,CEurovision: positives for Liverpool
OL,4,Cand BBC News coverage
