OL,6,FI suspect Eurovision will do more
OL,7,Flasting good to Liverpool than it
OL,8,Fwould have done to runner-up  Glasgow
OL,9,F` a city which has faced similar
OL,10,Fchallenges to Liverpool but which has
OL,11,Fplayed host to much more significant
OL,12,Fevents than Eurovision in recent
OL,13,Fyears such as the Commonwealth Games
OL,14,Fand COP 26.
OL,16,FBut this has been a strange
OL,17,FEurovision Song Contest.
OL,19,FIn recent decades, it has had a
OL,20,Freputation in Britain as "the show
OL,21,Fyou love to hate".
OL,3,CEurovision: positives for Liverpool
