OL,6,FBBC audience research always pointed
OL,7,Fto this paradox. It's very rare to
OL,8,Fcombine high viewing figures and a
OL,9,Fvery low audience appreciation score.
OL,11,FGiven its reputation as either as a
OL,12,F"festival of camp" or a complete
OL,13,Fturkey, some will have wondered
OL,14,Fwhether BBC News programmes should
OL,15,Fhave given so much coverage this week.
OL,17,FOf course, the BBC itself is rightly
OL,18,Fpromoting a major event which it
OL,19,Fplays a huge part in.
OL,3,CEurovision: positives for Liverpool
