OL,6,FIt must be a revelation to some
OL,7,Foutside the UK that the organisation
OL,8,Fbehind one of the world's biggest
OL,9,Fnews organisations ` responsible for
OL,10,Fso much excellent coverage of the war
OL,11,Fin Ukraine and providing honest
OL,12,Finformation to countries with state-
OL,13,Fcontrolled broadcasters ` is also
OL,14,Fpart of showbusiness.
OL,16,FI wonder what those unfamiliar with
OL,17,FRussia editor Steve Rosenberg's
OL,18,Fskills as a pianist and deep
OL,19,Fchildhood love of the BBC must have
OL,20,Fbeen thinking about his piano
OL,21,Frecitals in Liverpool this week.
OL,3,CEurovision: positives for Liverpool
OL,4,Cand BBC News coverage
