OL,6,FBut this all brings us back to why
OL,7,FBBC News has been right to treat
OL,8,FEurovision as a major story this year
OL,9,F` not an "and finally" or a bit of
OL,10,Ffun on Breakfast.
OL,12,FAs Steve himself explained, for some
OL,13,Fin the former communist countries it
OL,14,Fwas a symbol of western freedom.
