OL,6,FThis year's contest is, of course,
OL,7,Fbeing held in the UK on behalf of
OL,8,FUkraine. It holds a genuine
OL,9,F political importance this year `
OL,10,Fstrange as that may seem to those who
OL,11,Fcannot stand the contest. It
OL,12,Fsymbolises Ukraine keeping its
OL,13,Ffreedom alive.
OL,15,FStill BBC News has got to be careful
OL,16,Fto ensure that the upbeat tone of
OL,17,Fmuch of the coverage doesn't
OL,18,Finadvertently slip into becoming
OL,19,Fpromotional for the contest.
OL,3,CEurovision: positives for Liverpool
OL,4,Cand BBC News coverage
