OL,6,FWherever the BBC's corporate concerns
OL,7,Fbecome news, there is no better test
OL,8,Fof the corporation's journalistic
OL,9,Fstandards than the way these are
OL,10,Freported.
OL,12,FWhen a positive BBC event is in the
OL,13,Fnews this set of principles applies
OL,14,Ftoo.
OL,16,FThere's a difference between how BBC
OL,17,FNews covers Eurovision and, say, what
OL,18,FThe One Show has done to add to the
OL,19,Fbuild-up.
OL,3,CEurovision: positives for Liverpool
