OL,6,FThe last time Britain hosted
OL,7,FEurovision in 1998, there wasn't much
OL,8,Fnews coverage ` perhaps a look at the
OL,9,Fpreparations on Breakfast News and
OL,10,Fthe Six and a straight piece on the
OL,11,Fday itself.
OL,13,FThe next time Britain hosts,
OL,14,Fhopefully it will be in normal
OL,15,Fcircumstances and it won't be big
OL,16,Fnews.
OL,18,FBut this year's contest is part of a
OL,19,Fmuch more serious story.
